summary: This appears to be an FBI communication regarding the upload of a file related to an individual's date of birth, likely as part of the Epstein investigation. The document is a notification of a file upload from FBINET to UNET.

events.title: File Upload Notification
events.description: An FBI communication indicates a file was uploaded from FBINET to UNET. The attached file's name suggests it contains information about an individual's date of birth.

keyFacts: An FBI file related to an individual's date of birth was uploaded from FBINET to UNET on August 17, 2020.
The communication about this upload was sent on October 6, 2020.
The document is part of the Epstein case files, indicating the FBI was processing or sharing biographical data relevant to the investigation.
